Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:13.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:17.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:20.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,turned to rubber after \Nhe ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:22.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a pirate \Nalliance with Trafalgar Law
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:38.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and have come to Dressrosa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:42.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy entered a fighting competition \N- in which a winner will get the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.83,0:03:44.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Flare-Flare Fruit as the prize \N- and won the first round{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:47.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but now, he's heading for the palace to take
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:49.14,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,back Law who's been captured by Doflamingo.{\i0}
