Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sticky-Sticky Chain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stick-Stickem...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Meteora!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Trebol-{\i1}sama{\i0} is going crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Executive Tower has been destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:27.47,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,THE ROYAL PALACE B-1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We keep getting blocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you! Pica can manipulate\Nthis whole stone palace any way he likes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he really going to be okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:05:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be fine no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca has never made an attack \Nbefore but she just did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of sword is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its blade is blunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ring is a place for killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't cut anybody,\Nyou'll have to shed your own blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:07:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's what the people want to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a direct hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The undefeated girl couldn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diamante!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Musclemelon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.00,0:07:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm Bartolomeo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca, do you know\Nhow your mother Scarlet died?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go buy something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Toy Soldier cried like a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was so pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:07:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't protect your mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.87,0:08:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Trebol-{\i1}sama{\i0} do this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.97,0:08:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Robi...\N--Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:09:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What just happened?!\NI saw a big duck falling from the ceiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain to you later. We have a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo and the others got caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You prick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop dead! Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna die, you little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're having a serious conversation now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NDon't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.06,0:09:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know someone is helping you - who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey! What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Never, ever tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run while we can, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he's actually my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly, his name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Usoland?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! He's not my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! I've been fooled!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the one-legged soldier \Nyour associate, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not gonna tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if you know, then it can't be helped!\NHe's our associate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.32,0:10:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I thought so!\N--Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we see some connections!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter anymore!\NYou people are finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the decisive day!\NWe will pull off...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this operation no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.47,0:11:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we will...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...take back our friends at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sticky stuff is flammable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trebol-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.94,0:12:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.39,0:12:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo! Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.13,0:12:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me! That was too reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The operation is over! Let's run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you have to fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys did all you can!\NBut you can't beat Trebol!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not an option!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must complete Operation SOP...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.85,0:13:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as soon as...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the commander will...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...take down Doflamingo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The commander is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...waiting for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lao G, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lao G's "G"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"G"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"G"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:06.88,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,DRESSROSA - THIS MORNING
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DON QUIXOTE DOFLAMINGO\NWITHDRAWS FROM THE SEVEN WARLORDS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo-{\i1}sama{\i0} withdraws\Nfrom the Seven Warlords?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he gonna step down\Nfrom the throne of Dressrosa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's nothing but an ordinary pirate now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna be chased by the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, we're free!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, did you see the newspaper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means we're gonna have our friends back,\Ndoesn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.34,0:16:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We no longer have to fight Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NThat's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a false report.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad that it was just a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a great man!\NHe's not gonna abdicate the throne!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna enter today's competition\Nand win the Flare-Flare Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will take down Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca! Come to your senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.93,0:17:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So am I! But don't jump the gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna rise up! We're locked and loaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.79,0:17:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm not gonna wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our hopes have been dropped\Nfrom heaven to the edge of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one here can take it anymore!\NTheir spirits are broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All there is left to do is\Nwait to be executed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be released if we \Ncan win a thousand times?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NThat's not hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a wall of despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The legendary gladiator Kyros won\N3000 out of 3000 matches?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody knows that statue is\Njust make-believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dying prisoners must have made up\Ntheir ideal warrior and that's Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They built the statue\Nwishing to be freed like him someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not dream an impossible dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's competition is a \Nchance and I'll take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.70,0:18:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for you \Nto win that competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.61,0:18:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna die!\NI won't allow you to enter it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not thinking straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're only 16!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think of yourself \Nas an adult now, Rebecca?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still a kid!\NYou must listen to what I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please! You're not even my parent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's not thinking straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your plan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no chance to beat Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...just a one-legged toy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for being meddlesome\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I hope you're not gonna \Nenter the competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.21,0:19:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean it! Soldier-{\i1}san{\i0}, don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Soldier-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.75,0:19:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just afraid that\Nyou were gonna sacrifice yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! Don't go, Soldier-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.89,0:19:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Soldier-san!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's shaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be Pica! What is he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.64,0:20:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.49,0:20:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Commander?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let's get going!\N--Wait! They're gonna get beaten up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let go of me! You little bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop looking back, Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.76,0:20:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were planning on\Nsacrificing ourselves from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.76,0:20:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen if you stop here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Leo and the others \Npulled off Operation SOP,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.21,0:20:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if we let Doflamingo walk away,\Nhe'll turn everything back again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.32,0:20:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who can bring \Ndown Doflamingo, Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:21:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you care about the commander, Leo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you guys count on him so much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.46,0:21:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if only he makes it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.97,0:21:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just a one-legged toy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, people who are turned into toys\Nare bound by the contract
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they will become \Nworkers who can't disobey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The commander was the first person
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.86,0:21:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ever in this country to get turned into a toy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.37,0:21:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the Hobby-Hobby Fruit eater, Sugar...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.82,0:21:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...made a mistake forgetting\Nto make a contract!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.85,0:21:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one mistake from ten \Nyears ago made him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the only toy in this country who\Ncan get back at...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.61,0:21:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Don Quixote Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.60,0:22:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he's been fighting\Non his own for a decade!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.29,0:22:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't for him,\Ntoys would have no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.36,0:22:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but to put up with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We Tontattas wouldn't know anything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.97,0:22:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we all would have been enslaved by them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.41,0:22:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we ignore his rallying cry,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.86,0:22:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there'll be no chance of saving this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.84,0:22:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's worth betting everything on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.43,0:22:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody remembers him now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.83,0:22:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nbut everybody knew him once!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.27,0:22:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he was a Big Human, his name was...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.95,0:22:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.68,0:23:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the strongest gladiator\Nin the history of the Colosseum!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.85,0:23:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's who our commander is!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.76,0:23:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Toy Soldier runs to reach Doflamingo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.00,0:23:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but a brutal enemy named Gladius stands\Nin his way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.64,0:23:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When the Toy Soldierfs life is at stake
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.66,0:23:37.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to Gladiusfs overwhelmingly \Ndestructive power{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.46,0:23:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy rushes in like the wind!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.40,0:23:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.85,0:23:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,!\N"The Rupture Human! Gladius Blows Up Big Time!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.57,0:23:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.96,0:23:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
